{"tid":1816600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「一個抽獎睇穿曬某部分人智商」","createTime":"2020-01-08T10:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:19:10.000Z","uid":209382,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f354e58c3d037d1205585cd3e66da8cf8c7890c5","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"自問自己係搞抽獎個條友既話<br />\n唔會突然拎接近6-7位數金錢出黎搞所謂「抽獎」<br />\n<br />\n幫手share過抽獎post既人<br />\n比著係你，你會唔會咁做？<br />\n答唔會既話，咪撚自己呃自己話：「唔怕啦，話唔定中呢，抽唔中都無損失既。」<br />\n<br />\n推測搞抽獎個條友既目的<br />\n好大機會借<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">假抽獎</span></strong>推高自己post既人氣<br />\n再而進行進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自於佢下一步行動係咩<br />\n先係我地需要唸既野</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s. 人往往相信錢財會突然無緣無故降臨自己身上，<br />\n而往往忽略得到錢財背後所需付出既力氣。"},{"pid":"cbd32da8f6c4db6281de4523bb6d86a01a726f0f","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"BTW唔好話6-7位數既金額啦<br />\n<br />\n有d人你叫佢拎2-3位數出黎捐比612等既組織<br />\n佢都唸前唸後啦"},{"pid":"699d9600f8e207d40b086f1544e96a19161ddd34","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5fa0b61022c4721bc78b781dd0523eaf862c373","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"95697553c183449c08aa5cae7402ac49d653cf34","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8719c62d85c26f9fac58cb2211d353fc557e2896","tid":1816600,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"低智力淘汰係物競天擇一部份"},{"pid":"4f42598bb2702c04b709347e97cec217bdc4f057","tid":1816600,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb09665c818d18a01958ba06536b83872bcb1a32","tid":1816600,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"唔好笑ig啲人住 睇下連登有幾多個政府抽獎post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔都未必係好聰明"},{"pid":"332283cf99d4b0e1cae16a1b41fe1b1bfb934ae8","tid":1816600,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:01:37.000Z","msg":"【借位宣傳，與主題內容無關】<br />\n<br />\n試下用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「冇雙普選就獨立 / 沒有普選唯有獨立」</strong></span>做口號<br />\n<br />\n牌面上你係爭取緊無人有異議既雙普選。實質上你提供緊清晰既路徑，解釋緊點解要獨立、以及為獨立提供正當性。<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非，一開始可以則重係「雙普選」上面。但潛移默化地灌輸佢地獨立既可行性。對於獨派，亦解決左「時機」問題；因為嚴格上口號並唔係直接提倡獨立，但同時宣傳緊獨立。"},{"pid":"dade022fb9bcac5e6fa98ef5a1161d88e93bb12b","tid":1816600,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"236c9fe97e9154fc9a91b2281c337e62eeda2cba","tid":1816600,"uid":318802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"抽獎果d野一件都幾千蚊<br />\n無啦啦有條友彈出黎話送幾百件出黎，正常都應該會懷疑下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399a054b87084cfe932efd0324ffbb79d52309e4","tid":1816600,"uid":209382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"236c9fe97e9154fc9a91b2281c337e62eeda2cba","tid":1816600,"uid":318802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"抽獎果d野一件都幾千蚊<br />\n無啦啦有條友彈出黎話送幾百件出黎，正常都應該會懷疑下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"整係頭等5個都要最少成球野"}]}